## Time Estimates

| Points | Solo Dev | With Review |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | 1-2 hours | 2-4 hours |
| 2 | 2-4 hours | 4-6 hours |
| 3 | 4-8 hours | 1 day |
| 5 | 1-2 days | 2-3 days |
| 8 | 2-4 days | 3-5 days |
| 13 | 1 week | 1-2 weeks |
| 21 | 2+ weeks | Break down first |

**Includes:** Development + testing + code review

