## Quick Estimation Template

```markdown
## Estimate: [Task Name]

**Story Points:** [1/2/3/5/8/13]
**Time:** [X hours/days]
**Confidence:** [High/Medium/Low]

### Risks
| Risk | Level | Mitigation |
|------|-------|------------|
| [Risk 1] | Medium | [Action] |

### Assumptions
- [Assumption 1]
- [Assumption 2]
```

